ELITE

The official ELITE cheat. When asked for the code word from the 
manual, type SARA. Now type in the correct word when prompted and 
begin play. Press the  *  key on the numeric pad to access the hacker screen,
where bytes and variables can be changed to suit.

CHANGE BYTE          FOR

  32 to 01          Cloaking Device 
  31 to 01          ECM Jammer
  20 to 01          Escape Capsule
  23 to 01          Energy Bomb
  24 to 01          Energy Unit
  26 to 01          Docking Computer
  28 to 01          Galactic Hyperdrive
  80 to 01          Document
  84 to 01          Fugitive Rating
  85 to 01          Offender Rating
  88 to 01          Mostly Harmless Rating
  88 to 01-08       Poor - Elite rating
  1F to 01          Fuel Scoop
  34 to 03          Cargo Hold
  7C to 01          Unhappy Refugees

Press ESC to get back to the game.
