size of the game.  Have some fun and press the "ALT" key then "D" then
"Return or Enter" (I think twice) then type in either GET OBJECT (and type in
a random #) or "TP" for transport (and a random #) and see what happens.  It
works., and if you're tired looking for a certain object the "Get Object"
function works great!
