LIGHT CORRIDOR

First a little hint: The green diamonds are essential as these award you
with an extra life. Some of the red diamonds will allow control over two
bats but this is more of a hinderence as the two bats prove confusing.
Avoid the blue squares as they will shrink the size of your bat.

