NINJA SPIRIT

Press F9, then press Caps lock, then left shift. Game will continue with
infinite lives.
___________________________________________________________________________

NINJA WARRIORS:

Press the CAPS-LOCK and type in one of the following cheat codes, don't
forget to include the spaces! Press CAPS-LOCK again to turn it off and
activate the cheat mode:

NOTE: One Magazine says you hold down the ALT key while typing following:

   THE TERMINATOR- Causes the ninja's body parts to explode when he dies
   MONTY PYTHON- The enemies come on facing backwards
   SKIPPY- Causes the enemies to bounce around the screen
   A SMALL STEP FOR A MAN- Initiates moon gravity, anything that jumps leaps
                           off the top of the screen
   STEVE AUSTIN- begin playing and press S,toggles slow motion mode
   MAY THE FORCE BE WITH YOU- infinite stamina
   WARP FACTOR ONE MR SULU - level skip (keys 1-16 to corresponding level)
   CHEDDAR- unlimited credits
   GENESIS OF DALEKS - photo-negative screen mode.
