POWERMONGER

Instruct your captain to invent something, pause the game, put the game
speed up to full, and wait a couple of minutes. Now unpause the game, the
captain will have kept inventing during the pause!

When you wish to invent in double quick time, click Invent and when your
men leave, click on it again. This often makes a catapult immediately.
This cheat works only once on each island.
