    Where to get what and how: 
 
    Bouncing bombs - Castron depot, use on Projector bases only. 
 
    Missiles - Millway depots, use on Walkers, Stompers, etc... 
 
    Cuboids - use a lot of energy, given to you by prof Taymar. 
 
    Neutron bomb - use on space station only. 
 
