TRAINED ASSASSIN
Let the demo start then press and hold down '2', '4', 'Y', the left
cursor key and '7' on the numeric keypad for infinite lives. Also
hold down 'A', 'T', '.', '4', and 'ENTER' on the numeric keypad. 
Now 'F1' - 'F5' changes the level.
