TURRICAN

This is more of a bug than a cheat, but here is a technique you can
use in Turrican:
If you come to a bad guy that you don't want to deal with, leave the
screen and then come back.  The bad guy should be gone.  Unfortunately
this also happens to extra men and weapons.

(cheat)
To get 99 lives:
Get a high score more than 20,000  and quit game.
It will go to the high score table. TYPE "BLUESMOBIL" and hit return.
On the next play you will see 99 lives on the bottom of the screen.
__________________________________________________________________________

TURRICAN II

On the title scrren, tap the HELP key which will bring up the music menu.
Select Option one, Then select it again before pressing the numbers 4 and 2.
Now just press ESC twice to enter the game, and you now have infinite lives.
